Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.34,0:02:02.35,Background,,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't that Touya?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.05,0:02:04.85,Background,,0,0,0,,He's wearing a uniform from Kaiou!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:07.55,Background,,0,0,0,,I read about him in a Go magazine once...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:10.76,Background,,0,0,0,,Everyone's waiting for him to join\Nthe pros because he's a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.18,0:02:13.27,Background,,0,0,0,,What's a guy like that doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.74,0:02:15.07,Background,,0,0,0,,Isn't he an Insei?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.26,0:02:18.41,Background,,0,0,0,,I thought Inseis couldn't go\Nto Amateur competitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.84,0:02:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya is a member of Kaiou!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.65,0:02:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, aren't we playing Kaiou in the first round?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya said he is the third board.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.34,0:02:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What!? Third board!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.39,0:02:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to play him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.19,0:02:45.06,Background,,0,0,0,,So you're the Shindou Hikaru that\NTouya's always talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.52,0:02:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone that even Touya looks up to,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to your game with Touya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're from Kaiou.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.80,0:03:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you guys are good,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.64,0:03:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but you lost to Haze Junior earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.51,0:03:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.43,0:03:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be playing Kaiou in the second round.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.04,0:03:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll win too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you plan on winning\Nagainst Kishimoto-kun!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.08,0:03:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.27,0:03:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He plans on winning by cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsutsui-san, Mitani-kun wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.09,0:03:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsutsui?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the guy that got lucky against us earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.85,0:03:39.99,Background,,0,0,0,,He was so angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.99,0:03:42.41,Background,,0,0,0,,He lost because he missed something really simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.12,0:03:45.34,Background,,0,0,0,,Winning by cheating, or winning by luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.34,0:03:47.58,Background,,0,0,0,,What a great team Haze has.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.07,0:03:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitani-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just a freshman who's only playing\Nfirst board to try to con a win, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.24,0:03:59.01,Background,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by con a win!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.52,0:04:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitani is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitani is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.71,0:04:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,he's only a freshman, but he's\Nten times better than I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.95,0:04:08.56,Background,,0,0,0,,He is our first board!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:11.48,Background,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.37,0:04:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the first board, Kishimoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to playing you in the second round.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make it a game suitable for the first board.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.32,0:04:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Talk to us after winning the first round.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... we have to win the first round.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I only told the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,you're our first board so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you're good so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.04,0:05:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,don't cheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.28,0:05:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's begin now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:20.97,Background,,0,0,0,,Anyone currently in a game,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.97,0:05:22.84,Background,,0,0,0,,please stop and put your stones away.
