Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:32.07,Background,,0,0,0,,Well, will each school go to your assigned seats as they are announced?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.57,0:05:36.90,Background,,0,0,0,,First is Ayu Junior High against\NHamachi Junior High in seat A
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawahagi Junior High against\NTai Junior High in seat B
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.01,0:05:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Iwana Junior High against\NHaze Junior High in seat C
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.18,0:05:47.49,Background,,0,0,0,,Kaiou Junior High against\NSawara Junior High in seat D
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:04.87,Background,,0,0,0,,I'm black.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.59,0:06:18.17,Background,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.30,0:06:59.23,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He's fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:04.31,Background,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:13.79,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HC5FEC1&}Look, I'm so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:19.21,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Even Tsutsui-san, who dislikes me,\Nsaid that I was ten times better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.56,0:07:23.26,Memory,,0,0,0,,Let's make it a game suitable for the first board.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.86,0:07:25.72,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HC5FEC1&}Fine, we'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.64,0:07:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.46,0:07:51.41,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Already!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go watch Kaiou.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:36.20,Thinking,,0,0,0,,The old men from the Go salon developed\Ntheir own style of play but him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.56,0:08:48.72,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HC5FEC1&}Junior High clubs are this good!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.97,0:09:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.57,0:09:24.21,Background,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.88,0:09:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you learn anything? Mitani-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.40,0:09:41.35,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.96,0:09:47.53,Thinking,,0,0,0,,This guy thinks that I'm a weak little freshman\Nwho's only playing first board for strategic purposes too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:50.28,Thinking,,0,0,0,,That handshake was just to be polite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:53.61,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He doesn't care about his game against me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou's not doing well in his game right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.91,0:10:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsutsui-san, I promise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stop cheating for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.37,0:10:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to play against Kishimoto of Kaiou.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't you lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:29.55,Background,,0,0,0,,Damn, I'm not doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.63,0:10:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Haha, I've just about won!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.02,0:10:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You laughed!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.84,0:10:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't laugh until the game's actually over!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.35,0:11:24.83,Sai,,0,0,0,,These children, they've all\Nchanged from coming here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.11,0:11:28.96,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru is growing... steadily.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.07,0:11:33.71,Sai,,0,0,0,,But Hikaru isn't the only one who's growing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.07,0:11:38.76,Sai,,0,0,0,,Touya Akira he is as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.88,0:12:54.96,Background,,0,0,0,,White 72 and a half moku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.72,0:12:57.72,Background,,0,0,0,,Black 56 moku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:12:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,By 16 and a half moku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.69,0:13:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.31,0:13:06.64,Background,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.21,0:13:09.64,Background,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.31,0:13:23.41,Background,,0,0,0,,I resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.62,0:13:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:30.08,Background,,0,0,0,,You took your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Yun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it would calm myself down a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.63,0:13:39.42,Background,,0,0,0,,Haze Junior High won 3-0.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.56,0:13:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw Shindou's game?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.35,0:13:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll know once you play him.
