Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.43,0:14:00.28,Background,,0,0,0,,We'd like to break for lunch now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.57,0:14:02.74,Background,,0,0,0,,The afternoon session will begin at 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.18,0:14:07.16,Background,,0,0,0,,Hitaka, wanna go grab lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's grab Touya too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.91,0:14:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitaka
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.07,0:14:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I talk to you for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru! Lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.84,0:14:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.05,0:14:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.01,0:14:23.18,Background,,0,0,0,,Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.97,0:14:42.44,Sai,,0,0,0,,That was a splendid come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Wasn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.70,0:14:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my strength! Mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.33,0:14:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a lot better than I was before!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:55.92,Sai,,0,0,0,,But you still can't beat Tsutsui-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.46,0:14:59.92,Sai,,0,0,0,,Your next opponent is finally Touya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm playing him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.09,0:15:04.59,Sai,,0,0,0,,You don't have to come out and say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care how much Touya wants to play you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.52,0:15:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The team from Haze Junior High\Nis Tsutsui-san, Mitani, and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not a part of it Sai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.79,0:15:19.48,Sai,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.32,0:15:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't Touya come after I've gotten better?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.95,0:15:31.45,Background,,0,0,0,,And? What do you want to\Ntalk about Kishimoto-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.98,0:15:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,About Touya getting bullied?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it really happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.80,0:15:38.58,Background,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.81,0:15:42.13,Background,,0,0,0,,Touya was a loner in the club...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They wanted to either shame\NTouya, or chase him out of the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.54,0:15:52.47,Memory,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.77,0:15:56.06,Memory,,0,0,0,,4-9 huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.61,0:16:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But no matter how shamed he was,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya probably wouldn't have left the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.93,0:16:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.26,0:16:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.45,0:16:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The look on Touya's face as he faced Mr. Yun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:15.25,Memory,,0,0,0,,Weren't you going to make me third board!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.77,0:16:19.88,Memory,,0,0,0,,You said it yourself that I was the only\None who stood a chance against Shindou!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:25.46,Memory,,0,0,0,,Then I'll quit the club after this tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:27.93,Memory,,0,0,0,,Touya...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:29.55,Memory,,0,0,0,,Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:31.43,Memory,,0,0,0,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.39,0:16:34.18,Memory,,0,0,0,,you're the third board.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.13,0:16:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He knew how selfish he was acting,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,so it must have been hard on him too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:43.19,Background,,0,0,0,,Touya's quitting the club?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:44.48,Background,,0,0,0,,After today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.11,0:16:49.28,Background,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure the club'll\Nsettle down with Touya gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.56,0:16:50.98,Background,,0,0,0,,Yeah right
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.46,0:16:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you're disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.24,0:16:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted to play against\NTouya more than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya got bullied...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.09,0:17:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess he had it coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.83,0:17:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He only thinks of himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.18,0:17:15.15,Sai,,0,0,0,,But Touya isn't the type of\Nperson who's disliked by others.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.06,0:17:19.60,Sai,,0,0,0,,He probably swallowed his\Npride to become third board.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:22.60,Sai,,0,0,0,,He should of course be first board.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He's only thinking about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.01,0:17:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.85,0:17:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You play.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.28,0:17:40.37,Sai,,0,0,0,,Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.47,0:17:44.92,Sai,,0,0,0,,You said that you wanted to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.34,0:17:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You play.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.08,0:17:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You were here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.22,0:17:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The second round's about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure you don't want any food?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.10,0:17:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll eat after the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.25,0:18:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Tsutsui-san and Mitani?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.94,0:18:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They're playing, against each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.90,0:18:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.60,0:18:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitani-kun's excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He says he's going to gather his strength\Nand stomp down on the Kaiou first board.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.45,0:18:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsutsui-san's just as motivated too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.12,0:18:21.20,Background,,0,0,0,,First and second boards really should be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.76,0:18:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So you should be excited too, Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back, the afternoon's going to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.14,0:18:40.02,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you... you play.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.61,0:18:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He is very determined,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.94,0:18:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,if you worry about me, you'll lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:19:01.24,Sai,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll probably have to go all out on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.24,0:19:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.83,0:19:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't eaten?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.61,0:19:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you really play Kaiou without eating anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.28,0:19:40.74,Background,,0,0,0,,Please stop any games you're playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.88,0:19:43.12,Background,,0,0,0,,We're about to start the second round.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.78,0:19:49.08,Background,,0,0,0,,Schools that have been called upon\Nshould go to the seat they're assigned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.34,0:19:51.80,Background,,0,0,0,,Seat A is Kaiou Junior High\Nagainst Haze Junior High.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.95,0:19:54.42,Background,,0,0,0,,Seat B is Ayu Junior High against Tai Junior High.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.14,0:19:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.34,0:19:55.40,Background,,0,0,0,,Now for the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:58.09,Background,,0,0,0,,Seat F Kaiou Junior High\Nagainst Sawara Junior High.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiou Junior High and Haze Junior High right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.92,0:20:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We came all this way, aimed for Kaiou.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if we lose, let's just do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.57,0:20:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitani is here too after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But I might win out of luck again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.74,0:22:12.32,Sai,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fs45\bord2.5\shad1}Umezawa Yukari's\NGo Go Igo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.74,0:22:12.32,Background,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Igo!
