Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.31,0:22:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, we're at the Japanese Go Institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.31,0:22:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to participate in the Hikaru\Nno Go, Beginners Go Class today.
