Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.18,0:22:31.98,Background,,0,0,100,,I'm Mai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.21,0:22:33.54,Background,,0,0,100,,I'm Yuuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.61,0:22:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the class started, Teacher Yukari,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.11,0:22:39.53,NoteArialEF,,0,0,0,,{\pos(332,320)}Teacher Yukari, and various other\Npros will teach you the game!
