Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.49,0:22:50.66,NoteArialEF,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,341)}Look at the "Yuugen no Ma"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.25,0:22:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,or visit the "Yuugen no Ma" and it was a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.26,0:22:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come if you get a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.50,0:22:55.00,NoteArialEF,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,341)}Thank you to all of the pros who came!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.65,0:22:57.37,NoteArialEF,,0,0,0,,{\an2}To be continued.
